videos.description: Ahmaad Rorie shows off the handle and finishes with the midrange jumper.
videos.headline: Montana guard destroys defender's ankles with crossover

videos.description: Led by Jacob Davison's three 3-pointers, the Eagles shoot a blistering 61.5 percent in the first half of the Big Sky Championship.
videos.headline: Eastern Washington drills 8 3s for 11-point halftime lead

videos.description: The Grizzlies go on a 28-4 spurt to turn an 11-point halftime deficit into a 17-point lead late in the game.
videos.headline: Montana uses big run in second half to take control

videos.description: Grizzlies head coach Travis DeCuire breaks down the second-half adjustments made against Eastern Washington, how they fell behind and what the win means to him and his team.
videos.headline: Montana coach DeCuire: We have a lot of believers here

videos.description: Michael Oguine scores 21 points to lead Montana to an 82-65 win against Eastern Washington to advance to the NCAA tournament.
